                <p>LUJE.net is a small network located in Amsterdam, the Netherlands.</p>
                <p>
                    LUJE.net has an open peering policy.<br>However there is strict IRR filtering and RPKI. Filters are generated every hour.<br>
                    The provisioning of the configuration is done automatically from PeeringDB, please ensure your entry is kept up-to-date including IP addresses and number of prefixes announced.
                </p>
                <p>Please contact hostmaster [at] luje.net, use the <a href="/portal/">Peering Portal</a> or check out <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.peeringdb.com/asn/212855" target="_blank">PeeringDB</a> and <a rel="noopener" href="https://bgp.tools/as/212855" target="_blank">BGP.Tools</a>.</p>
